    Statistics for all Loops in VSM object

    vsm.hystStats.Rd

    This function loops through all hyst loops in VSMdata using vsm.hystStats() and adds those parameters

    This function loops through all hyst loops in VSMdata using vsm.hystStats() and adds those parameters

    vsm.hystStats(obj)

vsm.hystStats(obj)

    Arguments

    obj

    VSMdata object

    Value

    list

    list

    Author

    Thomas Gredig

    Examples

    filename = vsm.getSampleFiles()[1]
d = vsm.import(filename)
t(vsm.hystStats(d))
